text_with_dna: The clock ticked, a relentless rhythm in the sterile lab. Coffee stained manuals lay scattered across the bench, a testament to long hours and late nights. The faint hum of machinery filled the air, punctuated by the occasional beep of a timer.  Finally got the string, now run the simulations.
